        Constructor to insert Gamedata
        Parameters:
        riotid - Parameter for match id from Riot Api (parameter type: Long)
        ingameName - Parameter for player name which player uses in game (parameter type: String)
        champion - Parameter for name of the champion which was used in the game (parameter type: String)
        kills - Parameter for kills which were made by the player (parameter type: Long)
        deaths - Parameter for all the deaths player encountered during the game (parameter type: Long)
        assist - Parameter for all the assists player made throught the game (parameter type: Long)
        winlose - Parameter of the end result of the game (parameter type: String)
        position - Parameter to the players in game position (parameter type: String)
        rank - Parameter for the players rank (parameter type: String)
